[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]‘
[normal]Action for Roads
[normal]’
[normal] has
[normal] set out the Government’s plans for reforming the Highways Agency, making it more efficient, more secure, and giving it the freedoms needed to match the best performance in the private sector. 
